<main aria-labelledby="title" class="container py-4">
    <div class="bg-light p-5 rounded shadow-sm mb-4">
        <h2 id="title" class="display-6">About the System</h2>
        <p class="fs-5">The Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS) is a web-based prototype designed to automate the submission and approval workflow for independent contractor claims.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>System Features</h3>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item">✔ <strong>Automated Calculation:</strong> Eliminates manual math errors during submission.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔ <strong>Verification Algorithms:</strong> Automatically flags claims that exceed policy limits.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔ <strong>Digital Invoicing:</strong> Streamlines the generation of payment documents for HR.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">✔ <strong>Secure Access:</strong> Role-based authentication for Lecturers, Coordinators, and Managers.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

